997
01:06:32,200 --> 01:06:34,930
Apa pun itu, tunda saja dan biarkan anak-anak...

998
01:06:34,930 --> 01:06:36,130
Tidak bisa.

999
01:06:36,700 --> 01:06:38,200
Pernikahan kami lebih penting.

1000
01:06:39,439 --> 01:06:41,910
Astaga.

1001
01:06:42,269 --> 01:06:43,340
Kalian

1002
01:06:44,209 --> 01:06:45,479
