1003
01:06:46,079 --> 01:06:47,180
Ya.

1004
01:06:47,780 --> 01:06:50,380
Kami baru saja akan mengumumkannya.

1005
01:07:01,329 --> 01:07:02,360
Pertama,

1006
01:07:04,800 --> 01:07:08,030
